Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.86,0:00:06.11,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{Let's strike a blow, Kaido. - OG}Let's knock them into next week, Kaido.{Z}
Comment: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.32,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:11.28,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{I wonder how many of those five will survive. - OG}How many of those five\Ndo you think will survive?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:17.58,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,Trafalgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:21.58,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,{Can't you move either of them\Ndownstairs with your ability? - OG}Can't you move one of them\Ndownstairs with your ability?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:23.80,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,If I could, I would've done it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:28.13,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{Their haki is too strong, I can't move them! - OG}Their haki's too strong. I can't move them!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:31.34,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,{Then, let's tear them apart! - OG}In that case, let's disassemble 'em.{nao+Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.10,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey! Here comes a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:10.34,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{I hope your legs are\Nnot weakened yet, old bag! - OG}Hope your hips still work, you old hag!{Polly+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:13.80,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{Who do you think you're talking to, brat?! - OG}Who do you think\Nyou're talking to, smart aleck?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:24.02,Main-207+,Kaido+Linlin,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}– Conquest of the Sea!\N– Conquest of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.28,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\t(1693,0,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}{This can't be real! - OG}You've gotta be kidding me!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:35.95,Main-207+,Killer,0,0,0,,{\t(2269,0,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}{No! We can't dodge it! - OG}No way! We can't dodge that!{nao+Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:50.55,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{Get away! You guys! - OG}Get outta here, guys!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:02.89,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{If you don't get away... - OG}If they keep this up...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:05.36,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{we'll be wiped out! - OG}we're all done for!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:07.57,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:32.63,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{They're gone, but I can still hear them... - OG}I can't see them,\Nbut I can still hear them...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:36.09,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{They got away from it... I'm impressed. - OG}They must've escaped. Color me impressed.{nao+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.72,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,Zoro{-ya}, are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:44.85,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:47.61,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,{Good job blocking it even for a moment... - OG}Nice work blocking it for as long as you did.{nao+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:49.32,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:50.98,Main-207+,Killer,0,0,0,,Where's Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:02:59.37,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.71,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.63,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Red...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.80,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{You dodged it, Kaido! - OG}Why'd you dodge, Kaido?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.10,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{Must be because it hurts! - OG}Was it gonna hurt?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.19,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.59,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{Nice! Burn! - OG}Excellent! Burn!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:23.14,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{Burn more! - OG}Let the flames rise!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.93,Main-207+,Pirate,0,0,0,,{Damn! It's not going out at all! - OG}Dammit! They won't go down!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.68,Main-207+,Pirate,0,0,0,,{Why do we keep having problems?! - OG}We have enough problems as it is!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:34.94,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{Fukurokuju! You know where they store\Ntons of explosives, don't you?! - OG}Fukurokuju! You know where they keep\Nall those explosives, don't you?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:37.32,Main-207+,Fukurokuju,0,0,0,,{Yes, I'll show you the way. - OG}Indeed. Allow me to show you the way.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:41.36,Main-207+,Denjiro,0,0,0,,{There are flames! What's happening?! - OG}Everything is ablaze! What is going on?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.83,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,Go to hell, Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:48.58,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{Screw the New Onigashima Project! - OG}And take your\NNew Onigashima Project with you!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:49.95,Main-207+,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.29,Main-207+,Denjiro,0,0,0,,{So you did this! - OG}This was all your doing?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:54.67,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{Oh, there you are. - OG}Ah, so you finally show your faces!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:57.04,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{The Kozuki's half-ghost bastards! - OG}The half-ghost vermin of the Kozuki!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.38,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{What the hell do you want?! - OG}What are you even here for?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:04.14,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{For twenty years, you've endured tirelessly, - OG}For twenty years,\Nyou've gone to hell and back,{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:06.60,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{and followed me all the way here! - OG}and now you've followed me all the way here!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:10.43,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{Is that how much you hate me? Resent me?! - OG}Is that how much you hate me?\NHow much you resent me?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:12.06,Main-207+,Fukurokuju,0,0,0,,Lord Orochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:15.27,Main-207+,Fukurokuju,0,0,0,,{They don't know that you died once. - OG}They are not aware that you've died once.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:16.73,Main-207+,Fukurokuju,0,0,0,,{Please run. - OG}Please make your escape.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.11,Main-207+,Fukurokuju,0,0,0,,{Let me handle the– - OG}I shall dispose of–{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.23,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{Back off, you fool! - OG}Butt out, you simpleton!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.86,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,You're covered in cuts and bruises...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.62,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,No wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:28.74,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{You voluntarily came to your deaths! - OG}You ran willingly to your own deaths!{Polly+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:32.58,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{You must be out of your mind! - OG}You guys must be completely\Nout of your minds!{Polly+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:35.83,Main-207+,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,{Orochi! We do not have time\Nfor a fool like you. - OG}Orochi! We have no time\Nto waste on a fool like you.{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:36.96,Main-207+,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.71,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{What'll happen if I say no? - OG}And if I refuse?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.34,Main-207+,Denjiro,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:58.11,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{Do you guys know who you're messing with?! - OG}Do you have any idea\Njust who it is you're defying?!{nao+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:00.52,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{You have to know your place! - OG}Know your place, rodents!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:03.74,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{I'm the shogun of Wano! - OG}I am the shogun of Wano!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.82,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{What's that attitude?! - OG}What's with that look?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.37,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{I haven't done anything wrong! - OG}I've done nothing wrong!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:15.41,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{I only took my revenge on the Kozuki Clan\Njust as they deserved! - OG}All I did was take revenge on\Nthe Kozuki as they rightly deserved!{nao+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:18.50,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{I just took back what was\Nsupposed to be mine! - OG}I only took back\Nwhat was stolen from me!{Polly+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.39,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{But you idiots don't understand! - OG}But you oafs just don't get it!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:33.93,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{Citizens and samurai are supposed to\Nbow before their shogun and follow him! - OG}Citizens and samurai alike are meant to\Nbow before and obey their shogun!{Polly+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.19,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{I am a man of power! - OG}I'm the one with the power here!{nao+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.86,Main-207+,Raizo,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Flower Shuriken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:46.53,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{This country that oppressed me is to blame! - OG}It's all because this country oppressed me!{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.29,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,Th-That look in your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:03.50,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,Are you trying to tell me that I'm wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.88,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,Don't look at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.17,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:10.34,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,{I'm not wrong! - OG}I can't be wrong!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:15.27,Main-207+,Orochi,0,0,0,,Stop looking at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:27.36,Main-207+,Fukurokuju,0,0,0,,Lord Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.57,Main-207+,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,{I will leave your punishment to hell! - OG}Your punishment will be decided in hell.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.37,Main-207+,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,{Let's go! - OG}Onward!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.91,Main-207+,Raizo,0,0,0,,{Are you gonna avenge your lord? - OG}Will you avenge your lord?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.67,Main-207+,Raizo,0,0,0,,{I raised my opinion of you, Fukurokuju! - OG}I thought too little of you, Fukurokuju.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:43.59,Main-207+,Raizo,0,0,0,,{Even though he was a moron,\Nyou stayed loyal to him till the end... - OG}Foolish as he was, you remained\Nloyal until the bitter end.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:46.55,Main-207+,Fukurokuju,0,0,0,,{I can say the same to you guys! - OG}I could say the same to all of you!{nao+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:51.09,Main-207+,Fukurokuju,0,0,0,,{Even without my goal of vengeance,\Nyou and I are destined to fight! - OG}Even had I not sought vengeance,\Nyou and I would be destined to fight!{nao+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:53.18,Main-207+,Raizo,0,0,0,,{Do you know what I mean, Raizo?! - OG}I'm sure you understand, Raizo!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:54.18,Main-207+,Raizo,0,0,0,,{Yeah! - OG}Indeed!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.22,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{Let's go! - OG}Let's do this!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.98,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{Don't underestimate me, brat! - OG}You asked for it, whelp!{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.17,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{I won't let you do that! - OG}Not gonna happen!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.34,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{Doesn't matter if you come all at once! - OG}Come all at once for all I care!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.14,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{Go attack! - OG}Give it to him good!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.52,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,You shithead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:45.69,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.12,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:12.97,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Conqueror of Three Worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.64,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ragnaraka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:27.06,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:30.07,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{Let's finish off the others, too! - OG}Let's mop up the leftovers, too!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.16,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,{It's done! - OG}It's ready!{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:35.87,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.07,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.53,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:42.83,Main-207+,Zeus,0,0,0,,{Where am I?! It's dark! - OG}Where am I?! It's so dark!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:44.37,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.38,Main-207+,Killer,0,0,0,,{Can you do it, Roronoa?! - OG}You got this, Roronoa?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:49.50,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{I have no choice! - OG}I'd better!{Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.30,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{I won't let you go back to her! - OG}You're not getting back to her!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:11:00.22,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Flame-Rend: Crossing the Six Paths!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:06.15,Main-207+,Napoleon,0,0,0,,{Stop! I'm just a sword! - OG}Quit it! Come on, I'm just a sword!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:08.98,Main-207+,Zeus+Prometheus+Napoleon,0,0,0,,– Mama, help!\N– Mama, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.07,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:10.86,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,{Now's our chance! - OG}Now!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:12.61,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Punk Pistols!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.53,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{What's this?! - OG}What now?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:21.49,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{Did you think you could beat me\Nif you tore us apart?! - OG}You actually thought tearing us apart\Nwould be enough to beat us?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:30.92,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Repel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.55,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Takt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.35,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{You fool! - OG}You nitwit!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:41.72,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{You can't beat me by hitting me with a rock! - OG}You think a rock is enough to finish me?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.39,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:50.86,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{Oh, damn! - OG}Crap!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.24,Main-207+,Zeus,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:01.41,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{If she can't get help,\Nwe'll have one dropout! - OG}If she can't get help, then that's one down!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:05.50,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{How's that?! - OG}How do you like that?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.17,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{Help me now! - OG}Come help me!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.17,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.22,Main-207+,Zeus,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:20.64,Main-207+,Zeus,0,0,0,,What's going on, Mama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.81,Main-207+,Prometheus,0,0,0,,{Mama! I'm on my way... - OG}Mama! I'm coming to–{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.61,Main-207+,Prometheus,0,0,0,,{Mama! I'll come... - OG}Mama! I'm gonna–{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.45,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{\t(1485,0,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}{That fool. - OG}That moron...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:54.92,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{He could've had every bone in his body\Nshattered from that! - OG}I wouldn't be surprised if he shattered\Nevery bone in his body back there!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:59.26,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{That's pathetic, Linlin! - OG}That was pathetic, Linlin!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:03.14,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{Do I have to do everything for you? - OG}I have to do everything myself.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:07.81,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,Hey, Pirate Hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:11.19,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{Let Prometheus go! - OG}Release Prometheus!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.15,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:21.53,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Injection Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:28.70,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{Your ability unsettles me! - OG}You've got one hell of a strange ability!{nao+Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.87,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,Trafalgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.29,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Antibacterial Curtain! - OG}Curtain!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.43,Main-207+,Prometheus,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:44.01,Main-207+,Napoleon,0,0,0,,{Go away! - OG}Stay away!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:45.68,Main-207+,Prometheus,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.14,Main-207+,Prometheus,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.81,Main-207+,Prometheus,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.23,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,Hey, Traffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.28,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{That fire thing... - OG}Fire-face there...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:02.15,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,is gonna save Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.12,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{Let him go... - OG}Just let him go...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.33,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{I'd rather the mission failed... - OG}I'd rather the mission be a failure...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:15.13,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,than have one of us die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:26.10,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,{Our objective is to tear\NBig Mom and Kaido apart! - OG}All we wanted to do was\Nseparate Big Mom and Kaido!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:31.02,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,{You don't have to risk your life for it! - OG}No need to put your life on the line!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.19,Main-207+,Kid,0,0,0,,Leave Big Mom to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.83,Main-207+,Prometheus,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:50.54,Main-207+,Prometheus,0,0,0,,{I'm relieved, Mama! - OG}I'm glad you're safe, Mama!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.21,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{You're so cute! - OG}Aren't you just the sweetest?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:15:00.42,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,Prometheus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:03.30,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{On the other hand... - OG}Unlike {\i1}somebody{\i0}...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:06.72,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{What is Zeus doing?! - OG}What the hell is Zeus doing?!{nao+Gord+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:09.10,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{He's so useless! - OG}Useless little airhead!{nao - haha get it}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.10,Main-207+,Prometheus,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:15.81,Main-207+,Prometheus,0,0,0,,{agree, Mama! - OG}couldn't agree more, Mama!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:19.48,Main-207+,Prometheus,0,0,0,,{He's always clumsy and slow. - OG}He's such a klutz, always lagging behind.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.23,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,{You're right! - OG}You said it!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:27.20,Main-207+,Prometheus,0,0,0,,{Hey, hey, I need to ask\Nyou something, Mama! - OG}Hey, so, I got a favor to ask, Mama!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.12,Main-207+,Linlin,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:53.06,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,Look at Straw Hat's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:57.39,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{It's just like the last time! - OG}It's just like last time.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:01.36,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{He's passed out and is still... - OG}He's out cold, and yet...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:04.94,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{staring at me! - OG}he's still glaring at me!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:09.87,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{Should I... - OG}Should those eyes...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:13.08,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{smash those eyes first? - OG}be the first things I crush?{nao+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.29,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{Or... - OG}Or maybe...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:17.87,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,his brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.63,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{Or his heart? - OG}Or even his heart?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.59,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,Traffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:27.34,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,What I'm about to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.89,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,will push me to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.60,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,Zoro{-ya}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.31,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{Fighting sloppily... - OG}Dragging things out here...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:36.77,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{will only wear you down. - OG}is only wearing us down.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.15,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{If this doesn't work... - OG}And if this doesn't work...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:43.07,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{it'll be my time to die. - OG}then it's just our time to die.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.82,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{I'll leave the rest... - OG}After this...{Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:47.86,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{to you! - OG}it's all you.{Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.33,Main-207+,Zeus,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:09.13,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{He's our captain! - OG}That's our captain!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.89,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,Why don't you try...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:17.68,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{to smash my head first?! - OG}crushing {\i1}my{\i0} head first?!{nao+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:24.98,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Demonic Nine-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.15,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Asura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.91,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Blades Drawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.97,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Nine-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.83,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Asura: Blades Drawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:21.04,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Dead Man's Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.15,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.91,Thoughts-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{This brat... - OG}This kid...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.66,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{You possess... - OG}Don't tell me...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.83,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{the conqueror’s haki, too?! - OG}you've got conqueror's haki, too?!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.79,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{What are you saying? - OG}What are you talking about?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.42,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{I don't know what you're talking about! - OG}I don't know what you mean.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:17.80,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{I launched that attack with all my might! - OG}That was... my ultimate attack!{nao+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:25.60,Main-207+,Zoro,0,0,0,,{I wanted you to at least fall... - OG}Would've been nice...\Nif you'd at least fallen down...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:29.11,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{You should be happy... - OG}You've done plenty.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:31.69,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,This scar will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.50,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{What an annoying generation. - OG}This generation, I tell you...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:52.17,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,Hey! Zoro{-ya}, run!
Comment: 0,0:19:57.22,0:20:02.22,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,Don't bother approaching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:58.84,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{Don't bother approaching me. - OG}Don't trouble yourself.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:02.22,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{Don't bother approaching me. - OG}I'll just come to you.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:06.02,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Thunder Bagua!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.46,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,What a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:36.38,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{If you come with me,\Nwe can dominate the world... - OG}If you'd just come with me,\Nwe could've achieved world domination...{nao+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:38.76,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,With you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:41.47,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{We don't wanna be with you, idiot! - OG}We'd never join up with you, idiot.{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:48.48,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{We love the samurai. - OG}We love samurai.{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:55.78,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{I'll kick your ass at any cost! - OG}I'm gonna kick your ass, end of story!{nao+Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:02.28,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{You'll... - OG}You're...{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.37,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{kick my ass? - OG}gonna kick my ass, huh?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.96,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{Give it a try. - OG}Give it your best shot.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:16.59,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{If you think you can do it... - OG}As if your reckless fists...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.51,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{with your impulsive punches! - OG}would ever be good enough!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.64,Flashbacks-207+,Hyogoro,0,0,0,,Don't strain yourself!{Wano 21 - 09:11}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:34.69,Flashbacks-207+,Hyogoro,0,0,0,,It's a powerful force that is both\Nan invisible armor and a tool for offense.{Wano 25 - 20:49 ("It's" was added for here since its a fragment in 25)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.19,Flashbacks-207+,Hyogoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,268)}However, if you advance to the next level,{Wano 25 - 20:59}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:41.86,Flashbacks-207+,Hyogoro,0,0,0,,the haki that covers you\Nwill become even stronger,{Wano 25 - 21:03}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:46.03,Flashbacks-207+,Hyogoro,0,0,0,,reaching inside your opponents\Nand destroying them from within.{Wano 25 - 21:06}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.41,Flashbacks-207+,Hyogoro,0,0,0,,Don't strain yourself!{Wano 21 - 09:11; this ep - 24:00}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:54.38,Flashbacks-207+,Hyogoro,0,0,0,,Allow the unused haki in\Nyour body to flow to your fist!{Wano 21 - 09:13; this ep - 24:01}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:59.26,Flashbacks-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kong Gun!{Wano 56}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:07.89,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,It was still too shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.56,0:22:12.81,Flashbacks-207+,Hyogoro,0,0,0,,Power blooms in our darkest hour!{Wano 25 - 16:20}{needs fade maybe}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:18.57,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{I noticed something when I got\Nattacked by your spiked club. - OG}But after taking that hit\Nfrom your club, I figured it out.{Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:24.70,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{You can infuse yourself\Nwith conqueror's haki too, right? - OG}You can infuse things with\Nconqueror's haki, can't you?{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:33.25,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,How will knowing that help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:35.13,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{Can you do it, too?! - OG}Think you can do it?!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:49.35,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{Only a handful of strong men... - OG}Only the strongest...{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.35,0:22:52.93,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{can do it! - OG}can wield it like that!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:54.73,Main-207+,Kaido,0,0,0,,{You half-ghost bastard! - OG}You half-ghost rat!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:23:56.46,Flashbacks-207+,Hyogoro,0,0,0,,Don't strain yourself!{Wano 21 - 09:11; this ep - 21:54}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:00.38,Flashbacks-207+,Hyogoro,0,0,0,,Allow the unused haki in\Nyour body to flow to your fist!{Wano 21 - 09:13; this ep - 21:55}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.81,0:24:59.31,Main-207+,Law,0,0,0,,{He didn't touch him! - OG}He didn't even touch him!{nao}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.93,0:25:33.22,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.56,0:25:37.06,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,Traffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.06,0:25:41.52,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{Thank you for defending me. - OG}Thanks for watching my back.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.94,0:25:45.11,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{You two, go downstairs! - OG}Now head downstairs!{nao+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.57,0:25:49.07,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{I'll defeat him at any cost! - OG}No matter what else happens,\NI'm taking him down!{nao+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.66,0:25:57.62,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{Tell that to everyone... - OG}So go on...{nao+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.24,0:26:00.25,Main-207+,Luffy,0,0,0,,{for me! - OG}and let everyone know!{nao}
